  "texts": [
    "In order to enhance the coding's reproducibility, the IPIE recruited external people who were not involved in designing the coding frame [9].",
    "Since the data consists of collected articles and not raw personal data, external individuals could be involved while respecting the boundaries of ethical research.It is important to note that this ICR procedure does not guarantee \"objectivity\".",
    "As will be discussed in the Results section, the database can still be interpreted differently by different people depending on their background and personal experiences.",
    "Instead, this coding exercise aimed to establish reliability and validity, while refining the analysis by evoking dialogue between the external coders and the technical paper author.",
    "An additional aim of performing this ICR was to identify areas that needed clarification [10]."
  ],
